document_data.History:
The ''polymorph self'' spell was developed by [[variator]] [[arcanist]] [[Quantoul]] in [[-2021 DR|1838 NY (−2021 DR)]] under the name '''''Quantoul's selfmorph'''''.<ref>

By the [[1360 DR|1360s DR]] ''polymorph self'' was a common spell in the magical community of both [[Faerûn]]<ref> and [[Zakhara]].<ref>{{AQ-time}}

Around [[1372 DR|1372 DR, the Year of Wild Magic]], the spell fell out of use when the more versatile ''[[polymorph (spell)|polymorph]]'' was introduced in the Realms.<ref><ref group="note" name="3E">''Polymorph self'' was included in the ''[[Player's Handbook 3rd edition]]'', but in the [[Player's Handbook v.3.5|v.3.5 update]] the similar but distinct ''[[Polymorph (spell)|polymorph]]'' spell was used instead.
